data: {"type": "sql_query", "sql_query": "WITH weekly_visitor_counts AS (\n    SELECT\n        d.full_date,\n        SUM(f.swiss_tourists + f.foreign_tourists) AS total_tourists\n    FROM dw.fact_visitor f\n    JOIN dw.dim_date d ON f.date_id = d.date_id\n    WHERE d.year = 2023\n    AND d.season = 'Spring'\n    GROUP BY d.full_date\n)\nSELECT\n    full_date,\n    SUM(total_tourists) AS total_weekly_tourists\nFROM weekly_visitor_counts\nGROUP BY full_date\nORDER BY total_weekly_tourists DESC\nLIMIT 1;"}
